replies.body:
Even though I grinded Flex Q for maybe 30-40 games, and had it pretty much rolled back to disregard all my games, I just want to play, grind and improve in a competitive environment. It seems Solo/Duo is the only place I can do it as a solo player.

I even gave Flex Q a chance despite the majority disliking it, but of course it really screwed me over by ignoring my 30-40 games of try harding (yes i know its pre-season, but i really want to climb this season). It pretty much took away a week of my time and effort. 

Still love this game and don't mind this flex q "problem" too much, but I feel the people putting in the most time are getting the short end of the stick here. {{champion:32}}
